Cadillac Fixed Ops Marketing Client Spotlight

We are happy to have Cable Dahmer Cadillac!

In the Kansas City, MO market, Cable Dahmer Cadillac came on with Fixed Ops Digital in July of 2018. We set out to build beautiful high-ranking pages on their main CDK global website to Cadillac’s standards.

We have an exciting strategy for Cable Dahmer Cadillac in 2020 including recalls, dominating battleground cities, model specific service landing pages and more.

Examine a full year of automotive SEO stats from their Google Analytics below![/vc_column_text][image_with_animation image_url=”7084″ alignment=”center” animation=”None” img_link_target=”_blank” border_radius=”none” box_shadow=”none” max_width=”100%” img_link=”https://www.cabledahmercadillac.com/parts-department”][divider line_type=”No Line” custom_height=”32″][vc_row_inner column_margin=”default” text_align=”left” css=”.vc_custom_1573755775016{padding-top: 5px !important;padding-right: 5px !important;padding-bottom: 5px !important;padding-left: 5px !important;background-color: #eeeeee !important;}”][vc_column_inner column_padding=”no-extra-padding” column_padding_position=”all” background_color_opacity=”1″ background_hover_color_opacity=”1″ column_shadow=”none” column_border_radius=”none” width=”1/1″ column_border_width=”none” column_border_style=”solid”][vc_column_text]
